{
  "stem": "12882.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 19.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They looked new, but I had them for years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they wouldn't believe me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They thought I bought them black market or somewhere, and they said you come next morning to visit us at the Gestapo headquarter.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I did, and they beat the hell out of me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the one thing, which was left, is a slight hearing defect in my left ear which has not bothered me through my career because the-- it's in a frequency which was not the most difficult one.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I'm-- I have trouble with high voices.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now, I'm an old man, and hearing is the first thing which disappears-- or one of the first things.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I can't really claim anymore, but it is the hearing gets worse.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But so far, I still manage.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I have to bother other people to repeat their sentences.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Then-- this was life in Dresden.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We were shifted from one house to the other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then one day, it was all over, and we went to the Judensiedlung, S-I-E-D-L-U-N-G, in Hellerau, H-E-- double-L-- E-R-A-U.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That was very close to the place where the factory was where we worked, and then we watched every morning there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We marched back, and we lived in these barracks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And by then, my brother had changed his piano into an accordion and started-- I had still the violin-- and we made music there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He transcribed everything for accordion with a keyboard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we managed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But this wasn't for very long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We worked at [INAUDIBLE], as I said, and I actually a very agreeable work, nothing very difficult.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We made parts of a clock for a time bomb.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Now I know that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "When I did this little thing there, I didn't know what it was for.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But pretty soon, people told, and you found out.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
